Sidaa darteed, horumarinta daaweynta cudurka ayaa muhiim u ah in isbitaalada iyo rugaha caafimaadka ay si wanaagsan u isticmaali karaan adeegyada ama meelaha aan haysan qalab ku filan.
Iyada oo ku saleysan daraasadaha caafimaad ee la sameeyay illaa iyo hadda, waxyaabaha soo socda ayaa saameyn kara ama la xiriiri kara horumarka bukaannada COVID-19 (Shaxda (Shaxda 33):
Da'da: Da'da ayaa ah qodobka ugu muhiimsan ee lagu ogaanayo horumarka SARS, waana sidaas oo kale COVID-19.
