Si kastaba ha noqotee, waxay sidoo kale u baahan yihiin in la cusbooneysiiyo iyadoo la raacayo tilmaamaha ugu dambeeyay ee baaritaanka iyo daaweynta COVID-19 (Tijaabada Tallaabada Toddobaad) iyo daraasadaha ugu dambeeyay.
Sida ku cad daabacaadda toddobaad (3 Maarso 2020) xaqiijinta cudurka laga shakiyay waa in lagu daraa mid ka mid ah astaamaha taariikhda cudurka iyo laba astaamood oo cudurka ah si loo sameeyo falanqayn dhammaystiran, ama waa in lagu daraa saddex astaamood haddii taariikhda cudurka aan la hubin:
Taariikhda cudurka: (1) Safar ama joogitaan ku yimid Wuhan iyo aagagga ku xeeran, ama meel kale oo laga helay COVID-19 14kii maalmood ee la soo dhaafay ka hor inta aan calaamadaha soo bixin; (2) La xiriir la'aanta SARS-CoV-2 (oo ay weheliso tijaabooyinka nucleic acid); (3) La xiriir la'aanta bukaanada qandhada ama calaamadaha neefsashada ee Wuhan iyo aagagga ku xeeran, ama meel kale oo laga helay COVID-19 14kii maalmood ee la soo dhaafay ka hor inta aan calaamadaha soo bixin; (4) La xiriir la'aanta dadka ku nool aagga (in ka badan 2 bukaan oo qandho ama calaamado neefsashada oo la soo bandhigay 2 toddobaad gudahood, tusaale ahaan guriga, guriga, dugsiga, xafiiska, ama goob kale).
Calaamadaha cudurku waa: (1) qandho ama calaamadaha neefsashada; (2) calaamadaha muujinaya COVID-19; (3) tirada guud ee unugyada dhiigga cad ee muujinaya tirada unugyada dhiigga cad ee caadiga ah, oo aan kor u qaadin ama hoos u dhigin marxaladda bilowga.
Tijaabinta cudurka la xaqiijiyay waa inay ku saleysantahay shakiga cudurka ee muujinaya mid ka mid ah astaamaha cudurka ama astaamaha dhiigga ee soo socda: (1) Tijaabada PCR ee waqtiga dhabta ah ee muujisay SARS-CoV-2; (2) isku xigxiga qaybaha muhiimka ah ee fayraska oo muujinaya isku xirnaanta coronavirus cusub ee la yaqaan; (3) muujinta cudurka ee IgM iyo IgG-ga gaarka ah ee SARS-CoV-2 ee baaritaanka serum; ama isbeddelka astaamaha SARS-CoV-2 ee aan la gudbin cudurka, ama kororka hal mar in ka badan 4 jeer ee wareegga soo kabashada ee ka sarreeya inta lagu jiro xaaladda degdegga ah.
Waxaan u aragnaa in tijaabooyinka neefsashada ee nucleic acid ama tijaabooyinka dhiigga ee waqtiga la qaatay lagu daray buugga labaad (18 Janaayo 2020) iyo buugga saddexaad (22 Janaayo 2020).
Aqoonsiga cudurka ee tijaabooyinka dhiigga ayaa lagu daray daabacaadda afaraad (27 Janaayo 2020) iyo shanaad (8 Febraayo 2020); ka dibna astaamaha dhiigga ayaa lagu daray daabacaadda toddobaad.
