Quest Diagnostics waxay sidoo kale sameysey baaritaano COVID-19 oo dalka oo dhan laga heli karo laga bilaabo 9 Maarso 2020.
Ma jiro tiro xadidan oo la soo bandhigay; ururinta iyo qaabeynta shaybaarada la qaaday waa in la sameeyaa iyadoo la raacayo shuruudaha Xarumaha Xakamaynta Cudurrada (CDC).
Ruushka, baaritaanka COVID-19 waxaa soo saaray oo soo saaray Machadka Dawladda ee Cilmi-baarista Fayraska iyo Teknolojiyada Biology ee VECTOR.
