19-kii Maarso 2020, FDA waxay siisay rukhsad degdeg ah (EUA) Abbott Laboratories si ay u tijaabiso nidaamka Abbott m2000; FDA waxay siisay rukhsad la mid ah Hologic, LabCorp, iyo Thermo Fisher Scientific.
