Maalinta Caalamiga ah ee Gacmaha Nadiifinta waa tusaale kale oo olole ah oo lagu dhiirigelinayo dhaqidda gacmaha si loo gaaro ujeeddooyinka isbeddelka dabeecadda. Sababtoo ah cudurka faafa ee coronavirus ee 2019-20, UNICEF waxay soo saartay emoji-ga dhaqidda gacmaha.
