Si kastaba ha noqotee, hal daraasad ayaa muujinaya in kor u qaadista dhaqidda gacmaha saabuun ay ka waxtar badan tahay adeegsiga biyaha iyo nadaafadda kale.
Muhiimadda ay leedahay nadiifinta gacmaha ee caafimaadka aadanaha; gaar ahaan, dadka daciifka ah sida hooyooyinka dhalay ama askarta dagaalka ee isbitaalka ku jirta, waxaa lagu muujiyey bartamihii qarnigii 19aad iyadoo la adeegsanayo laba hormuud oo nadiifinta gacmaha ah: Ignaz Semmelweis oo ahaa dhakhtar reer Hungary ah oo ka shaqeynayay Vienna, Austria iyo Florence Nightingale, oo ah "abuure cusub oo kalkaalisadda".
Waqtigaas, dadka intooda badan waxay weli aaminsanaayeen in cudurrada faafa ay yihiin kuwa neefta.
