WHO waxay ku talineysaa in kaliya waji-xidhka caafimaadka loo xirto shaqaalaha soo-dhoweynta ee xarumaha kala duwan.
Dadka qaata baaritaanka neefsashada, daryeelayaasha, ama kuwa qaada bukaanka COVID-19 ee aan haysan hawo, WHO waxay ku talineysaa inay xirtaan maaskaro caafimaad, muraayadaha ama gogosha, dharka iyo gacmo-gashiyada.
