Maaddaama la yareeyo baahida loo qabo xirmooyinka ilaalinta shakhsiga ah (PPE) ee caalamiga ah, WHO waxay ku talineysaa in la yareeyo baahida loo qabo xirmooyinka ilaalinta shakhsiga ah iyadoo la adeegsanayo daaweynta la kala saari karo, in la sameeyo goobo isku dhafan sida daaqadaha la arki karo, iyo in la ilaaliyo adeegga daryeelka tooska ah ee qolka bukaanka COVID-19, in PPE la isticmaalo oo keliya marka loo baahdo shaqo gaar ah, in la sii wado isticmaalka hal neefsashada iyada oo aan la lumin waqtiga daryeelka bukaannada badan ee is dhex gala, la socodka iyo waxqabadka PPE iyo in la joojiyo isticmaalka waji-xidhka dadka aan calaamadaha muujin.
