Bishii Abriil, khubarada CEPI waxay ku dhawaaqeen in 10 tiknoolajiyo kala duwan ay ku jiraan cilmi baarista iyo horumarinta horraanta 2020 si loo horumariyo tallaal ka hortagga COVID-19.
Hababka la horumarinayo ee weli ku jira marxaladda I ee cilmi baarista waxaa ka mid ah:
Unugyada DNA iyo RNA ee daraasadda tallaalka ee marxaladda I waa: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
Unugyada fayraska (qiyaasta tallaalka ee wajiga I: CanSino Biologics, adenovirus type 5 vector)
