Daraasadaha ayaa ku fashilmay in lagu muujiyo gudbinta fayraska ee doofaarka, digaagga iyo digaagga.
Ma jiro daawo ama tallaal lagu xaqiijiyay in uu daweeyo cudurka.
Waxaa jira daraasado caalami ah oo ku saabsan tallaalada iyo daawooyinka COVID-19 oo ay wadaan hay'adaha dawladda, kooxaha aqoonyahannada iyo cilmi baarayaasha warshadaha.
Bishii Maarso, Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa bilaabay "SOLIDARITY Trial" si loo qiimeeyo saameynta afar daawo oo caadi ah oo la rumeysan yahay inay daaweyn karaan cudurka.
Wax tallaal ah lama helin, laakiin hay'ado kala duwan ayaa tijaabinaya tallaalo kala duwan.
Waxaa la isticmaalayaa daraasadaha hore ee SARS-CoV SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV-2 maadaama ay labaduba isticmaalaan ACE2 receptor si ay u galaan unugyada jirka.
Waxaa jira saddex tallaal oo la baarayo.
Marka hore, cilmi baarayaashu waxay rabaan inay sameeyaan tallaal ka dhan ah fayraska.
Isticmaalka fayraska, ha ahaado mid aan shaqeyn ama mid dhintay, waxaa loogu talagalay in lagu kiciyo nidaamka difaaca jirka ee qofka si loo ogaado cudurka cusub ee COVID-19.
Tallaabada labaad waa isticmaalka unugyada, taas oo loogu talagalay in lagu sameeyo tallaal kaas oo u oggolaanaya nidaamka difaaca jirka inuu ogaado jiritaanka unugyada fayraska.
Marka laga hadlayo SARS-CoV-2, cilmi-baarista ayaa diiradda saareysa qanjirka u eg ee u sahlaya fayraska inuu soo galo ACE2.
Habka saddexaad waa midka ku saleysan DNA ama RNA, oo ah qaab cusub oo lagu sameeyo tallaalka.
Noocyada tallaalka ee la baaro waa in la tijaabiyaa tayada iyo waxtarka. 16 Maarso 2020, afar mutadawiciin ah oo ku nool Seattle ayaa bilaabay tijaabinta tallaalka.
Tallaalka waxaa ku jira unugyo laga soo qaatay fayraska keena cudurka. Kor u qaadista difaaca jirka ayaa la soo jeediyay inay tahay habka ugu wanaagsan ee lagu horumariyo tallaalka SARS-COV-2, laakiin weli waxaa jira dhibaato.
In ka badan 300 oo tallaal ayaa la tijaabinayaa ilaa Abriil 2020.
Toddoba tijaabo ayaa lagu sameeyay daawooyinka caadiga ah ee loo oggol yahay daaweynta Duumada, oo ay ku jiraan afar hydroxychloroquine ama chloroquine.
Cilmi-baarista Shiinaha ayaa diiradda saareysa daawooyinka caadiga ah ee fayraska, iyadoo sagaal tijaabo oo wajiga III ah lagu sameeyay remdesivir, oo lagu soo bandhigay dalal badan oo kala duwan iyadoo la filayo in warbixinta la sii daayo dhammaadka Abriil.
Ilaa Abriil 2020, waxaa jira dib u eegis joogto ah oo ku saabsan tijaabooyinka COVID-19. Daawooyin badan oo caan ah oo loo isticmaalo daaweynta cudurrada fayraska ayaa loo baaray si loo daaweeyo COVID-19, kuwaas oo ay ka mid yihiin remdesivir, chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir iyo lopinavir/ritonavir oo lagu daray interferon beta.
Laga bilaabo Abriil 2020, waxaa jira caddayn muujinaysa waxtarka remdesivir.
Bukaannada lagu daaweeyay remdesivir waxay muujiyeen horumar.
Tijaabooyinka heerka III ayaa ka socda Mareykanka, Kanada iyo Talyaaniga. Chloroquine, oo mar kale loo isticmaalo daaweynta Duumada, ayaa la tijaabiyay Febraayo 2020, iyadoo natiijooyin horudhac ah la helay.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, waxaa jira baaqyo loogu talagalay cilmi baaris dheeraad ah.
Hay'adaha caafimaadka ee Kuuriya iyo Shiinaha ayaa ku talinaya isticmaalka chloroquine.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, Xarunta Caafimaadka ee Wuhan, iyadoo ku talineysa hal garaam maalintii, waxay tilmaamaysaa in labanlaabista qiyaasta ay keeni karto dhibaatooyin halis ah oo ay ku jiraan dhimashada.
28 Maarso 2020, FDA waxay si ku meel gaadh ah u oggolaatay dhakhaatiirta daaweynta bukaannada COVID-19 inay si qarsoodi ah u isticmaalaan hydroxychloroquine iyo chloroquine. Xeerarka 7 waxaa ka mid ah isticmaalka interferon, ribavirin ama umfenovir si loola dagaallamo COVID-19.
